utton\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 06, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cth1665702785978.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cth1665702785978.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cth1665702785978.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cth1665702785978\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Uniface IDE allows you to have two windows open at the same time. The secondary window cannot contain the output tabs. You can move an editor between windows using the editor tab's context menu.\n </p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"cth1665702785978__fig_d3611e1_d3612e1_d3613e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Switch Window Button</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Context menu for editor tabs\" class=\"image\" id=\"cth1665702785978__image_yqd_vwx_3zb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/editortabswitchwindow.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cth1665702785978__li_d1280e1_d1281e1_d1282e1\">To open the secondary window, right-click an editor tab (or the start page tab) and choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Move to Other Window</span> from the context menu.\n <p class=\"p\" id=\"cth1665702785978__p_d3614e1_d3615e1_d3616e1\">If there is no secondary window yet, it is automatically started and the editor is opened in the secondary window.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cth1665702785978__li_d1283e1_d1284e1_d1285e1\">To close the secondary window, you can:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cth1665702785978__li_d1286e1_d1287e1_d1288e1\">Click the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">X</span> button in the title bar of the window.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cth1665702785978__li_d1289e1_d1290e1_d1291e1\">When only one editor is open in the secondary\n                  window, right-click the tab and choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Close Editor</span> from\n                  the context menu.  <p class=\"p\" id=\"cth1665702785978__p_d3620e1_d3621e1_d3622e1\">The secondary window is\n                     automatically closed and focus is returned to the main window.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526606\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526606\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Open or Close the Secondary IDE Window Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 06, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The Uniface IDE allows you to have two windows open at the same time. The secondary window cannot contain the output tabs. You can move an editor between windows using the editor tab's context menu. Figure 1. Switch Window Button To open the secondary window, right-click an editor tab (or the start page tab) and choose Move to Other Window from the context menu. If there is no secondary window yet, it is automatically started and the editor is opened in the secondary window. To close the secondary window, you can: Click the X button in the title bar of the window. When only one editor is open in the secondary window, right-click the tab and choose Close Editor from the context menu. The secondary window is automatically closed and focus is returned to the main window. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}